flowchart TD
    A["HTTP Request"] --> B["NestJS Controller / Service"]
    B --> C["AOP Aspect<br/>@PreEnforce / @PostEnforce / @EnforceTillDenied / ..."]
    C --> D["SAPL PDP<br/>Policies (policies/*.sapl)"]
    D --> E["Decision<br/>PERMIT / DENY + obligations + advice + resource"]
    E --> F["Constraint Handler Bundle<br/>registered handlers matched by type"]
    F --> G["Response<br/>filtered / transformed / replaced / denied"]
